{"tid":1718890,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論]ONEPIECE 海賊王 ワンピース 962 大名和家臣 中文情報,圖","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:02:59.000Z","uid":3020,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"342f9c63a66721937e4c129046a2f699d0497b9e","tid":1718890,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNpGxFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNpGxFb.jpg&h=e0f78022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65nMJNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65nMJNa.jpg&h=43cae1c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gnyj3MR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnyj3MR.jpg&h=355d630e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第962話標題 大名和家臣<br />\n為了收服阿修羅童子禦田離開白舞，前往壽喜燒也不敢出手的犯罪者聚集地九里。<br />\n禦田離開後，金庫裡的錢不知所踪，犯人大蛇嫁禍禦田。<br />\n禦田一邊在和之國中大鬧，一邊向九里前進，仰慕他的人隨他同行。<br />\n禦田成功改造了九里，這一壯舉讓壽喜燒解除斷絕關係的命令，給予他九里大名的稱號<br />\n之後6年過去，此時大海上已經毀滅的洛克斯海賊團餘黨們正在聚集新的伙伴，揚名四海。<br />\n河鬆在九里海灘發現了不知是不是人的2人漂流至此。<br />\n<br />\n圖中文字<br />\n（右上）禦田：&ldquo;大名&rdquo;的身邊會有家臣跟隨！ ！ &hellip;&hellip;（看不見了）<br />\n眾人：&hellip;&hellip;（感動）<br />\n被毀滅的傳說&ldquo;洛克斯海賊團&rdquo;的殘黨們聚集了新的同伴，其後擴張勢力揚名海上&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【和之國&ldquo;九里的海岸&rdquo;】<br />\n河松：這是什麼？ ？動物？ ？毛很多的人類？ ？難道是異形怪物！ ？真讓人不舒服啊！ ！<br />\n【被打撈上來的兩人是&hellip;&hellip;！ ？ 】"},{"pid":"df1c8486418b06d23c5f8bc29883c7f5efdbb2bc","tid":1718890,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登嘅冷氣軍師，想幫手又冇得發夢嘅，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該幫手上Twitter，Reddit幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線搏晒老命同班警甴對抗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n美國議員繼續為香港發聲，大家快啲去回應支持啦～<br />\n<br />\n！！！提出法案嘅Marco Rubio話有好消息！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=650c0a42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187%3Fs%3D09&h=0bd235ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Marsha Blackburn 繼續撐香港！繁體中文出沒注意<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=1a992eb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&h=56d542bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Dick Durbin促請Leader McConnell 就法案進行投票！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=539cc2dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953%3Fs%3D09&h=dbd9a813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick Scott連發兩炮<br />\n！撐學生  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/119